	Keep the stars shining bright in your home and allow your incense fragrance to filter out evenly with this gorgeous soapstone white star incense burner. This delightful black incense holder will keep your incense stick burning evenly without having to worry about the mess afterwards. Made for burning incense sticks the bottle lid has a cork centre in which to insert your lit incense sticks. When placed back on top the incense then burns upward and the ash drops and is collected in the base. The star patterns on the sides of the bottle are numerous small holes which let the smoke and aroma from the incense escape evenly while looking great. Dimensions- 280mm tall.</p>
